**QA Measuring Tool**

This tool can be used to do quick and easy measurement checks of the manufactured tourniquet.
Just print the pdf file and cut it out around the solid line. 

https://github.com/GliaX/tourniquet/new/master/assembly_instructions/quality_control/tourniquet_measuring_tool.pdf

Here are photos of how the tool is used to measure various parts of the tourniquet during QA checks:

![For Box Stitch measurement](https://github.com/GliaX/tourniquet/new/master/assembly_instructions/quality_control/MToolBoxStitch.jpg "Box Stitch Measurement")

![For Bridge measurement](https://github.com/GliaX/tourniquet/new/master/assembly_instructions/quality_control/MToolBridge.jpg "Bridge Measurement")

![For Slack measurement](https://github.com/GliaX/tourniquet/new/master/assembly_instructions/quality_control/MToolSlack.jpg "Slack Measurement")
